Glenn SPRADLEY, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Julie JONES, etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1974 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 20, 2017 LAGOA, SCALES and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of mandamus and the response thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
